<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV52">
<l>poṟṟaiyuṟṟa muṟṟalyāṉai pōretirntu vantataip</l>
<l>paṟṟiyuṟṟu maṟṟataṉ maruppocitta pākaṉūr</l>
<l>ciṟṟeyiṟṟu muṟṟaṉmūṅkil mūṉṟutaṇṭa roṉṟiṉar</l>
<l>aṟṟapaṟṟar cuṟṟivāḻu mantaṇīra raṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Raṅgam with beautiful cool water, where those bearing the trident staff</l>
<l>[made of] mature bamboo with small teeth[-like nodes],</l>
<l rend="indent">—who have set their minds solely [on Him and] have renounced attachment—</l>
<l rend="indent">live considering [it highly],</l>
<l>is the town of the Mahout who moved towards and caught</l>
<l>the mature, forest-dwelling elephant, which came opposing [Him] in battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">and furthermore, broke [its] tusks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
